name: Earth Tunic
description:
100% cotton print on front with 100% cotton jersey at neck and back.
This is a loose and comfortable tunic that can be worn in any season. Looks great with long sleeves, leggings and ankle boots.
(Limited fabric - use contact page for custom sizing)

name: Felt Textured Skirt
description:
This winter skirt is felted on the inside, so lovely and soft and has an embroidered texture on the outside.
The Slight A-line of the pattern is quite flattering.
There is an invisible zip in the back and it sits just below the knees.
Looks great with boots.

name: Sixties Shift Dress

Contrasting pocket.

This dress is made in a beautifully soft. easy care, stretch knit fabric.
Almost feels like you are wearing your fave sweater - only a bit more dressy.
The belt is covered in the same fabric but it looks just as good without the belt.
The many colours make it easy to accessorise - just think of the shoes or boots that you could wear with it.
ONLY 3 MADE

name: Simple Striped Skirt
description: This is a lovely light, full skirt with an elastic waist and tie with belt loops. It would look equally at home in summer with a little top or in winter with leggings and a skivvy.

It can be worn with or without the tie and looks great over leggings for those cooler days. A delicate fabric - but easy to wash and no ironing required.

name: ABC Rug
description:
A lovely soft, warm, hand-knitted rug perfect for boys and girls.
A generous cot-size - makes a great snuggle rug to take anywhere. 
The rug is made from a good quality yarn (88% acrylic - 12% wool) so is easy to wash on the gently cycle of your washing machine.
FREE POSTAGE within Australia.

name: Up-cycled Easter Bunny
description:
These happy little easter bunnies are made from up-cycled woolen jumpers that I have felted. Each one is a little different and has a hand embroidered face and tail. The bunnies are filled with toy fill so can be machine washed when necessary. 
These are a perfect alternative to chocolate OR you could place an egg in bunny's arms and let your little diddums find "The Easter Bunny"
I hope you like them.

name: Lime/grey Wrap Dress
description:
A beautiful, comfortable, soft, stretch knit dress that is very versatile. The wrap style is great for all shapes and sizes and grows with your child. The tie can be worn at the back, side or front and the dress looks great alone or with leggings.
(As shown in photograph except with above elbow sleeves.)

The top layer is a lovely cotton linen with embroidered holes and the petticoat layer is soft and lightweight.
A lace trim is sewn onto the hem of both layers and the dress can be worn with the belt pulled snug at the waist or loose for an even more comfortable fit.
